## Key Learnings

* NumPy is the core library for numerical computing in Python.
* NumPy arrays are faster and more efficient than traditional Python lists.
* Arrays allow mathematical operations to be performed easily on entire datasets.
* NumPy provides built-in functions for creating and managing data efficiently.

